Class CiccarelliTaxonomyService

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.berkeley.compbio.phyloutils.RootedPhylogenyAsService<String>
      • edu.berkeley.compbio.phyloutils.NewickStringTaxonomyService
        • edu.berkeley.compbio.phyloutils.CiccarelliTaxonomyService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.davidsoergel.trees.TaxonMergingPhylogeny<String>, TaxonomyService<String>, TaxonStringIdMapper<String>, Serializable

    public class CiccarelliTaxonomyService
extends NewickStringTaxonomyService
    Reads a Newick tree file containing the Tree of Life (Ciccarelli 2006, http://itol.embl.de) and provides it as a RootedPhylogeny. Also provides convenience methods for a few common operations such as computing the tree distance between two species.
